{"tid":721843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ICAC?]中科老闆：禮頓要求刪工人剪鋼筋片段 爆料後7000萬工程無法中標　「港鐵出手唔俾我哋做」","createTime":"2018-06-29T03:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T15:09:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":79,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"8822abd65c063fea8a68257847b2a89d0605eedf","tid":721843,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"鐵沙中綫紅磡站鋼筋被剪短事件，分判商中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻，今早出席電台節目時，仔細談到揭發鋼筋被剪短的細節<strong>。潘焯鴻指出，中科曾試圖阻止工人「有系統地」剪鋼筋不果，去年初港鐵高層應已知悉事件，質疑港鐵包庇禮頓。潘焯鴻又說，中科去年9月18日曾與「補救方案」等，與禮頓達成協議後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">並在禮頓要求下，把在手機中的一段有人剪鋼筋過程的片段刪除。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">負責混凝土工序的中科在2015年7月開始注意到有鋼筋被剪短，潘焯鴻在台節目指，當時港鐵前線人員十分著力阻止事件發生，於是口頭與港鐵溝通，希望解決、改善。潘焯鴻指，曾親眼看到有工人「有系統地」去剪短鋼筋，並發現有人訂了可以剪得較快捷的「油壓剪」回來。「我見到，有人覺得這方法慢，於是買個『油壓剪』回來，明顯你買個剪就是個有思考、有planning的過程啦！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n曾親見鋼筋「有系統地」被剪短<br />\n<br />\n他指，剪短鋼筋是嚴重事件，曾嘗試阻止。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我們覺得是足以影響結構安全的，所以嘗試阻止，在阻止過程中，我們發現也無能為力、做不到，所以擔心在20至30年後，會不會我們俾人揪出來，因大部份工作是我們做，所以要我們負責呢？」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>他認為，禮頓負責的削石屎步驟出錯，是事件主因，是其後要由工人補救；其他原因包括石屎面螺絲頭方向不正確等。他指在這情形下，禮頓是要呈上補救方案給地鐵審批，然後根據方案執行。不過他指，地鐵至今沒有交代，禮頓有否呈上補救方案。對於以剪鋼筋去補救，是否不可接受時，潘焯鴻說：「是絕對不可以」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n他指，禮頓母公司協助港鐵在澳洲開拓業務，故相信是港鐵對禮頓，與對待其他承建商的態度截然不同的理由，質疑港鐵包庇禮頓。「究竟是否有人在包容港鐵？這連串包容，發展成包庇，這是可圈可點的。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻指出，港鐵報告中，提到2017年1月，當中科以書面電郵向工程總承建商禮頓高層投訴時，禮頓高層有將電郵轉發給港鐵，港鐵高層人員尤其是工程總監說不知情，是「可圈可點」的事。他提到，工程總監屬下一名外籍項目經理（胡宏利，港鐵總經理（沙中綫土木工程）），每周也會到地盤巡視，而潘亦有同行。「很清晰見到，其實2017年1月後，他（黃唯銘）不能說自己不知道。不可以這樣說。」<br />\n<br />\n指數千支鋼筋被剪   估算合理<br />\n<br />\n中科去年9月18日與禮頓達成協議，包括他們認為可行的「補救方案」，他指，當時相信不會影響整個完工時間，對協議感到滿意。當時潘焯鴻應禮頓要求，把在手機中的一段有人剪鋼筋過程的片段，即場刪除。當時又簽署一份罰則是較重的保密協議，協議的範圍基本上是有關事情都要保密，只有在三個情況下才可以披露：在法院的法官要求下、在聯交所要求下，以及要報稅時。若發現有資料泄露，也要通知禮頓。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻說，被剪短的鋼筋絕對不只十多支，主持人問到，潘指剪短鋼筋的數目足以影響紅磡站月台結構安全，如估計數目介乎幾百至一千支，甚至數千支是否合理，潘焯鴻回應說這個估算合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%8C%87%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B-%E6%9C%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%B0-%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%AA%E7%9F%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%88%AA%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%89%AA%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2589%25AA%25E7%259F%25AD-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2589%25AA%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=df134242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2589%25AA%25E7%259F%25AD-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2588%25AA%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2589%25AA%25E9%258B%25BC%25E7%25AD%258B%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%2F&h=b58dd5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%8C%87%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B-%E6%9C%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%B0-%E8%A2%AB%E5%89%AA%E7%9F%AD-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%88%AA%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%89%AA%E9%8B%BC%E7%AD%8B%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5/</a>"},{"pid":"7bab21068218f9a0ebd95f1aaf00c048a7aeabeb","tid":721843,"uid":83913,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"少有咁正直嘅公司<br />\n<br />\n希望佢無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eaadb79be22cb89c3f59960746018e31361a98","tid":721843,"uid":190540,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e5d3a0e4900928e1509ebbb63fb7dbd568a0dac","tid":721843,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"中科老闆：揭鋼筋被剪短後　7000萬工程無法中標　「港鐵出手唔俾我哋做」<br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫紅磡站鋼筋被剪短事件，最早揭露問題的分判商中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻，今早出席電台節目。潘焯鴻透露，中科揭發鋼筋被剪短的事件後，去年1月中科有一個價值7千多萬港鐵的工程幾乎中標，經已去到最後階段。後來他發現，最後中科沒有中標，「據我所知，是港鐵出手唔俾我哋做」。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻說，「（7000多萬元）那不是佔我們很多生意額，其實我們沒有停過做港鐵工程，那一刻我們都覺得心灰了，港鐵原來處事是這樣的，我們都沒所謂了。」<br />\n<br />\n港鐵昨日在報章刊登聲明，斥責有人單方面提出指控或揣測，「不必要地影響公眾對鐵路基建工程的信心」，更不點名批評判中科興業以及立法會議員田北辰。潘焯鴻指，中科角色始終是工程「二判」，很容易會令業界的人認為我們「搞事」，但港鐵出廣告「抹黑」公司是並不應該，而這廣告正是驅使他出來澄清。<br />\n<br />\n他指，覺得這工序「危險」和「離譜」，由當初希望口頭解決和改善，但事件到去年9月中科要離開地盤，這事件也未解決。他說。「這牽涉公眾安全，這也是良心問題，也牽涉我們同事將來的風險。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A08000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%25AC%25A08000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%2F&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e6b74a24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%25AC%25A08000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%2F&h=f77c081e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A08000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"e4e0be32e41d34b0d3e8808543a6acbf9b98cd8f","tid":721843,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"承認禮頓仍欠 8,000 萬元　中科老闆否認因此指控對方<br />\n<br />\n中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻打破多個星期的隠身，昨天開始突然高調現身各大傳媒，先後出現在D100、商台、港台及蘋果動新聞，對紅磡站懷疑鋼筋遭剪短事件現身說法。他在訪問中承認承建商禮頓仍欠中科 8,000 多萬元，但否認因此公開事件。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻指，由於港鐵星期三刊登聲明，指有人單方面指控對事件沒幫助，令他站出來澄清事件，「港鐵的說法似乎不是解決問題，是解決提出問題的人，這是很過份。」他指願意跟港鐵工程總監黃唯銘對質。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻在港台接受訪問時，亦直指事件中有人講大話，「其實出來講嘢的無乜幾個人(笑)」。主持再問他禮頓無出來發表過任何言論，只餘下港鐵和政府，潘焯鴻即時表示：「政府都無乜講過嘢！」他指政府只是評論事件，沒有任何事實陳述，對於港鐵的角色，他如是說：「我諗都唔駛我講啦，大家都聽到佢(港鐵)講過啲咩啦，日日變，甚至隔晚變，變完又變啦！」潘焯鴻的說法，明顯針對港鐵中人。<br />\n<br />\n而港鐵主席馬時亨未有回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A08000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%25AC%25A08000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%2F&d=McWGvGq8vZ1KCR0AbI8lrZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e6b74a24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%25AC%25A08000%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%2F&h=f77c081e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E4%BB%8D%E6%AC%A08000%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%91%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"a6147b6283ff79ac06b9009cd13619f78d691e1f","tid":721843,"uid":130262,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"如果帶住d機密資料搭車，落車唔記得左拎，又咁橋比其他人執到。咁算唔算違反保密協定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2d2498ac314f63b4635fecca1c95e84553fad9","tid":721843,"uid":48083,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"叫人刪除犯罪証據算唔算妨礙司法公正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074b8deba2a64b69a4aa4f7e2dafe18cde2f0b73","tid":721843,"uid":111153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"港鐵有咩做唔出"},{"pid":"69ca1d0bc1985ddf08f04693cbac1a19cde30c44","tid":721843,"uid":56453,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7bab21068218f9a0ebd95f1aaf00c048a7aeabeb","tid":721843,"uid":83913,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"少有咁正直嘅公司<br />\n<br />\n希望佢無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:12:01.000Z","msg":"child登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1ff88591e492f72795c952802e371baa13bd3b","tid":721843,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8979e78fafd6d5619f6f12a7e42e03d58c8c9e72","tid":721843,"uid":71635,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e8eaadb79be22cb89c3f59960746018e31361a98","tid":721843,"uid":190540,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"唔爆，就會做同水喉匠一樣坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},